casebody.data:
Peter Valdez CAHUE, petitioner,
v.
Jaded Mahelet Ruvalcaba MARTINEZ. No. 16-582. Supreme Court of the United States March 20, 2017.

Motion of The International Academy of Family Lawyers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
